content__image\"><img src=\"../../assets/images/img-works-people-page15.jpg\" alt=\"\"/>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"c-works-content__content\">\n                        <div class=\"c-works-content__category\">コーポレートスタッフ職（DX推進部）\n                        </div>\n                        <h3 class=\"c-works-content__head  c-heading is-xxs\">多様で魅力的な人たちと、DXを通して新しい健康価値の創造に挑む｡\n                        </h3>\n                        <div class=\"c-works-content__name\">D.U\n                        </div>\n                      </div></a>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"c-works-content__navigation\">\n                  <div class=\"c-works-content__right\">\n                    <div class=\"c-works-content__navigation-buttons\">\n                      <button class=\"c-works-content__navigation-button  is-prev js-swiper-prev\">chevron_left\n                      </button>\n                      <button class=\"c-works-content__navigation-button  is-next js-swiper-next\">chevron_right\n                      </button>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"c-works-content__stop\">\n                      <button class=\"c-works-content__navigation-button  is-stop js-swiper-stop\">pause\n                      </button>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"c-works-content__left\">\n                    <div class=\"c-works-content__count\">\n                      <div class=\"c-works-content__count-now  js-swiper-now\">\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"c-works-content__count-text\">/\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"c-works-content__count-all  js-swiper-all\">\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class